Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:48.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日未明　新たな魔法使いが\N再び現れました。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:48.23,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Earlier today, the new mage appeared again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.92,0:01:53.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（不破真広）≪吉野から\N聞かなきゃいけないことがある≫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.06,0:01:53.26,Defalics,,0,0,0,,There's something I have to ask Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.60,0:01:57.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[ﾃﾚﾋﾞ]（キャスター）本日正午過ぎ\N絶園の魔法使いと共に　今回も→
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:59.63,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The new mage appeared alongside the mage of Exodus again today, just past noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:00.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新たな魔法使いが現れました。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.38,0:02:03.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バシン！\Nガン！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.18,0:02:05.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:17.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪約束した以上は→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.22,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I promised,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:20.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次に会うときには\N言わなきゃならない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.96,0:02:20.30,Defalics,,0,0,0,,so I have to tell him the next time I see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.78,0:02:23.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[ﾃﾚﾋﾞ]（キャスター）\Nただいま入りました情報です。→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.10,0:02:23.15,Defalics,,0,0,0,,This just in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:26.90,Defalics,,0,0,0,,A mysterious flying fruit has been spotted in the sky near Akaiyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:26.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,赤城山上空で\N謎の巨大な果実が目撃され→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:29.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこには　絶園の魔法使いと→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:31.61,Defalics,,0,0,0,,The mage of Exodus was seen there with the new mage as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.04,0:02:32.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新たな魔法使いの姿も\Nあったとのことです。→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.34,0:02:35.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この果実は　以前からも\N目撃情報が寄せられており…。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.49,0:02:35.80,Defalics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,500)}Previously, we received information that similar fruits were sighted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.87,0:02:42.62,hv,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\bord3.8\3c&H624A21&\1c&H624A21&\pos(645,528)}The New Mage Is the "Dancing Princess"
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.87,0:02:42.62,hv,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8\c&HB8F5FD&\pos(645,528)}The New Mage Is the "Dancing Princess"
Dialogue: 2,0:02:36.87,0:02:42.62,hv,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\c&HE5F2F3&\pos(645,528)\alpha&H60&}The New Mage Is the "Dancing Princess"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:39.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[ﾃﾚﾋﾞ]　政府の通達に従い　以後→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.36,0:02:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Following a government notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we will now refer to the new mage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.60,0:02:42.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新たな魔法使いを\N舞姫と呼称します。→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}as the "Dancing Princess."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:46.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一連の事件に関し\N警察および　国防軍は→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:46.33,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Regarding these incidents, the police and the military
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:48.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,静観の姿勢を崩さず→
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.33,0:02:48.22,Defalics,,0,0,0,,continue to maintain their silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.21,0:02:51.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,関係各省庁への批判が\N相次いでいます。
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:50.80,Defalics,,0,0,0,,and the government faces mounting criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪吉野は…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:52.84,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.53,0:02:57.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（回想）((お前に　愛花ちゃんの彼氏が\N誰だったか教えてやる))
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:57.43,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the identity of Aika's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:01.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪真広は…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.66,0:03:00.92,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Mahiro,
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.88,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\pos(690,505)}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.88,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(690,505)}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.93,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.2\fs44\pos(640,96)}Episode 19
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.93,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\bord8\blur8\fs44\pos(640,96)}Episode 19
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.93,Title,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.2\pos(645,427)}The Object of Desire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.93,underTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\pos(645,427)}The Object of Desire
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.67,0:03:04.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（吉野・真広）\N≪覚えているだろうか≫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:03.41,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I wonder if you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.11,0:03:13.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）はぁ…　あの姫様は\Nなんちゅうことをしてくれたんや。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did that princess do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:17.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）おかげで　政府も\Nはじまりの樹破壊案には懐疑的だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.14,0:03:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to her, the government is now wary of the plan to destroy the Tree of Genesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well. I guess it's time to regroup with the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:21.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）いいかげん　あのお姫様とは\N合流したいところね。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:23.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）とはいえ\Nネックは　あの二人だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But the bigger problem is those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:25.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼は戻ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.85,0:03:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Has he come back yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.61,0:03:29.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）あれから　一度も。\N携帯も置いてっちゃったし。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not even once,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,though he even left his cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:33.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,問題ばかり増えていくな。\N（山本）ほんと　これ以上…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like one problem after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.52,0:03:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me about it. One more and—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.62,0:03:36.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パキーン！\Nキキーーッ！（ブレーキ音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,An attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:39.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,襲撃か!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:43.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（哲馬）\N張っていた結界が吹き飛んだ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.06,0:03:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We crashed through a barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,though you might as well call it an attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.18,0:03:46.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,襲撃といえば襲撃だが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:48.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）また問題が増えたわ。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the problems just keep piling up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.82,0:03:52.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪吉野に会って→
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:52.91,Defalics,,0,0,0,,When I see Yoshino
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:56.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花の彼氏が誰だったか聞いて\N俺は　どうする？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:55.99,Defalics,,0,0,0,,and ask him about Aika's boyfriend, what am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:58.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪どうしたいんだ？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:03:58.43,Defalics,,0,0,0,,What do I want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:08.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((おい　愛花　お前は　病弱な\N深窓の令嬢みたいな外見して→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:05.32,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Hey, Aika,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.32,0:04:08.34,Defalics,,0,0,0,,how come you look like a frail, sheltered "damsel"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:11.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして　そう\N格好も生活態度も雑なんだ？))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:11.09,Defalics,,0,0,0,,but act and dress like a slob?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:15.82,Defalics,,0,0,0,,That's because I'm neither frail nor sheltered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:15.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（愛花）((それは　中身が　病弱な\N深窓の令嬢ではないからですよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:18.27,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Besides, Mahiro,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.21,0:04:19.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（愛花）((真広こそ\N妹に自分の理想を→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:22.38,Defalics,,0,0,0,,trying to impose your ideals onto your sister is in rather bad taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,押しつけようなんて\Nとんだ悪趣味ですね))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.77,0:04:27.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((はぁ…　お前の今の姿の方が\N趣味悪いぞ))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:26.06,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Well, the way you're sitting now is in even worse taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.21,0:04:29.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((こういう私を認められたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.80,Defalics,,0,0,0,,When you can accept me the way I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.78,0:04:32.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広も一人前ですよ))\N((あっ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:31.72,Defalics,,0,0,0,,you'll be a real adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.99,Defalics,,0,0,0,,This, coming from a kid in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.83,0:04:35.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((中学生が生意気なこと言うな))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((その調子じゃ　お前→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.21,0:04:37.95,Defalics,,0,0,0,,At this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.95,0:04:40.68,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I doubt you'll find yourself a boyfriend any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:40.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当分　彼氏はできそうにねぇな))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.44,0:04:47.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（店主）はい　小倉あんが３つに\Nクリームが３つ→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.64,0:04:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, three with red-bean paste, three with cream,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:51.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと　豆乳クリームが２つね。\Nどうも。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and two with soy cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.10,0:04:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:56.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）なるほど。\Nはじまりの樹超兵器説に加えて→
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So on top of the theory that \Nthe Tree of Genesis is a superweapon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.12,0:04:59.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野に絶園の魔法使い疑惑…　か。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,there are allegations that Yoshino is the mage of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.18,0:05:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:02.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）驚かないのね。\N（葉風）言いたいことは分かるが→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.12,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand what you mean to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.88,0:05:05.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私が\N吉野に操られているとしたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but if Yoshino were really controlling me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:07.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ\N羽村を鍛えてやったりはせんよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.49,0:05:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't bother training Hanemura.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）はぁ…　それなんだけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しばらく\N舞姫は休んでくれない？→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.09,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you put off the "Dancing Princess" act for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanemura is worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:16.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羽村君　ボロボロだから。\Nと言っても…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:19.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカッ！\N（羽村）うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:22.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（潤一郎）\N考えるんじゃない。　感じるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.19,0:05:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:26.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）潤一郎君に　ジムで\N鍛え直されてるみたいだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.69,0:05:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Junichiro's been training him in the gym.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.47,0:05:30.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）さすがの潤兄さんも\N尻に火がついたか。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.52,0:05:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So even Jun is feeling somewhat motivated now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.12,0:05:32.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（早河）\Nどこぞの姫君のおかげですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All thanks to a certain princess we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.71,0:05:34.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）まあ　そう言うな。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.76,0:05:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,果実を飛ばす協力も\Nしたではないか。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I even helped you get a fruit to fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:41.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門殿は　果実を飛ばす準備に\N１年もかかったというのに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To think it took Mr. Samon an entire year to do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　私は姫様なのだよ　哲馬。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why {\i1}I'm{\i0} the princess, Tetsuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残る果実は一つだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.17,0:05:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one fruit left.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.08,0:05:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as the Tree of Exodus doesn't absorb it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:51.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを\N絶園の樹に吸収させんかぎり→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.74,0:05:56.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,樹は　完全復活せんし\N羽村の力も完全になるまい。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it cannot fully revive,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and Hanemura's power won't reach full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:06:01.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さて　多忙の早河を\Nつきあわせるのも忍びない。→
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.03,0:05:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.05,0:06:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no further reason to detain Hayakawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:04.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,場所を変えるか　フロイライン。\N（山本）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's change our venue, Fräulein.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.03,0:06:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）貴様の説を\Nゆっくり聞きたいのでな。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.82,0:06:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear your theory in much greater detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:10.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,喜んで。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:19.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）惑星が　ほかの惑星に\N侵略する能力を奪うための→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.34,0:06:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,One planet sent out weapons that destroy civilizations \Nto prevent other planets from becoming possible threats?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.75,0:06:22.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,文明破壊兵器か…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.96,0:06:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:26.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）そう　「文明破壊機」とでも\N名付けましょうか。→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.80,0:06:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we just call it the "Civilization Blaster"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,An unmanned weapon, programmed to destroy civilization once it has reached a certain point;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:28.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,文明が　ある段階に達すれば\N破壊するよう→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,プログラムされた無人兵器。→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A superweapon scattered across the universe to ensure that extraterrestrial lifeforms
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:35.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その生命体が生まれた星だけで\N穏やかに暮らすため→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,will remain confined to their home planets.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:37.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,宇宙にばらまかれた超兵器。→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That weapon is
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.59,0:06:40.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに対して付けられた名が→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree of Genesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.27,0:06:42.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹。→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あなたの神様。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,your god.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.15,0:06:50.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）鎖部一族も\N兵器システムの一環でしょうね。→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.29,0:06:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that the Kusaribe clan \Nis a part of this weapon system too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:54.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一族が供物として捧げる\N文明の産物をサンプルに→
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.42,0:06:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The clan provides samples of civilization as sacrifices to the Tree,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,which can determine how advanced the civilization has become.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.10,0:06:57.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その文明レベルを判断している…\Nとか。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:01.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふっ　あまりに想像を外れた話だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:07:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds pretty far-fetched to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:03.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,我々が使うのは魔法だぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What we use is magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of nature that governs all logic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:06.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理を統べる超自然の力だぞ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To portray that as an alien weapon is absu—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.83,0:07:10.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを　異星人の兵器だとするのは\Nいくらなんでも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.02,0:07:17.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あまりに進んだ科学は\N魔法と区別がつかない。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Once science evolves past a certain point,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.77,0:07:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to distinguish it from magic.{Arthur C. Clarke's third law, motherfuckers!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:19.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちが魔法と呼び　恐れる力は→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can you be sure that the power we fear as "magic"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.58,0:07:23.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,未知の科学の産物でないと\Nどうして言える？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't just the product of a science we don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:26.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,では　絶園の樹は　どう説明する？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then how do you explain the Tree of Exodus?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:29.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はじまりの樹の目的を妨害し\N破壊する樹が→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.17,0:07:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would a Tree that can interfere and destroy the Tree of Genesis
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.71,0:07:33.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ　同じ惑星に存在するのだ？\N（山本）そうね→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.73,0:07:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,exist on the same planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.29,0:07:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.87,0:07:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be that the two Trees were designed as one,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.88,0:07:37.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二つの樹は　最初から\N一つのものとしてデザインされ→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:41.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同時に地球に現れたとした方が\Nむしろ自然かもね。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.87,0:07:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and both appeared on the planet simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But that would make your \N"ultimate weapon" theory rather unlikely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.87,0:07:45.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすると　超兵器説は\N無理筋ということになるが。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:48.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,発想の方向性としては\N正しいと思う。→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I still think I'm on the right track,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:53.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが　どこかの何かが\N邪な意思を持って→
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,believing that thing out there was sent to our planet
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:56.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私たちの世界に\N侵入させたものだってことは。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,by someone or something with malicious intent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お土産　冷めちゃったな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.05,0:08:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotten all cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:09.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）貴様の説\Nはじまりの姫君としては→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.98,0:08:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,As the Princess of Genesis,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I must say I have mixed feelings regarding your theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.08,0:08:12.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,複雑な気分だが　同感ではある。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but I agree with the basic premise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.43,0:08:14.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも今\Nはじまりの樹は→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.51,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the Tree of Genesis lets me to control it, at least for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:18.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,曲がりなりにも\N私の制御を受けている。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.43,0:08:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If it has malicious intent,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:21.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,邪悪な意思があるにせよ\Nなぜ　そこに住む者によって→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,why allow someone on the target planet to control it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.87,0:08:24.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,制御が\N可能にされているのか…→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:26.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それも腑に落ちんしな。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:30.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ひとまず　お姫様は　冷静に\N物を見られているようね≫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.96,0:08:30.71,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Looks like the princess is still capable of thinking objectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）で　吉野君とは\Nうまくいってるの？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.59,0:08:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are things going well with Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）どうして　いきなり\Nそういう話になるのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How did we get to talking about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Tree of Genesis is an aggressor we must defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:43.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もし　はじまりの樹が\N倒すべき侵略者なら→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:46.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その姫宮である\Nあなたを殺すのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the one who may try to kill that aggressor's princess
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:48.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,絶園の魔法使いである→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,could very well be Yoshino, \Nassuming he is the true mage of Exodus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.47,0:08:50.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野君になるかも\Nしれないじゃない。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.65,0:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no definite proof that it's Yoshino,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:54.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ吉野だという確証はない。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:57.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが　そうだな→
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,but you do have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.03,0:09:00.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それはそれで　悪くない。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of itself, that wouldn't be so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ここのところは要注意か≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:03.17,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I guess we still need to be on alert...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:05.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪愛ゆえに　この姫様は→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.79,0:09:08.68,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Who knows what this princess could do in the name of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:09.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最後の最後で\N何をやらかすかしれない≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ほれた男のために死ぬって→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:14.18,Defalics,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}Still, to be willing to die for the man she loves is kind of sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結構　甘美だからね≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.51,0:09:16.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）そうだ　フロイライン。→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Fräulein, I'd like to make a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとつ　頼まれてほしいのだが。\N（山本）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.65,0:09:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.31,0:09:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you ask that Samon's barrel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.43,0:09:22.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,富士山麓から　左門の樽と→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.05,0:09:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and Mahiro's wooden doll be retrieved from Mt. Fuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:25.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広が使用していた\N木彫りの人形を回収するよう→
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.14,0:09:28.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,指示してもらえないか？\N（山本）樽と人形？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The barrel and the doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:42.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪何も答えない墓に\N何を願っている？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:41.45,Defalics,,0,0,0,,What's there to ask of an unresponsive grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪何を祈っている？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.63,0:09:44.19,Defalics,,0,0,0,,What's there to pray for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.34,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Saying anything after someone's death is too little, too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:49.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪死んでから何を言っても\N全部　手遅れだろ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.09,0:09:52.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪墓に参って\N何を慰められたがってる？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:52.11,Defalics,,0,0,0,,What kind of comfort can you get from a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪理屈に合いやしねぇ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:54.32,Defalics,,0,0,0,,It makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.04,0:10:00.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪そういや　吉野も…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.07,0:09:59.94,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Now that I think about it, Yoshino...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.21,0:10:07.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪やっぱり　俺には場違いだな≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.27,0:10:06.42,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I guess this was a mistake after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.97,0:10:10.64,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I thought that if I came here, I might change my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:11.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪こういう所に来れば　気分も\N少しは変わると思ったが…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:16.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪俺は\Nどう変わることを望んだ？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:16.18,Defalics,,0,0,0,,What kind of change was I hoping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:25.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰るか。\Nこんな所で　知った顔にでも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.42,0:10:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'll run into anyone I—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで　こんな所にいるんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.37,0:10:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:46.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いやいや\Nそれは　こっちのセリフだって。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.09,0:10:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I should be saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:49.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,自分の家の墓参りも\Nろくにしなかったお前が→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You rarely even visited the family grave, so why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:53.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうして…。\N散歩だ　散歩。　ほかに意味はねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.49,0:10:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? Why are {\i1}you{\i0} here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:59.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,で　なんで　お前は　ここにいる？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.07,0:11:01.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな　僕らに気を遣ってか→
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.27,0:11:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't had a chance to see you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別行動のままになってるからさ→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,since everyone's been giving us time apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:07.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さすがに悪いから\N僕から　お前に会いに→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.59,0:11:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt bad, so I thought I'd buy these
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:10.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手土産も買って\N近くまで来たんだけど…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.86,0:11:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to find you on my own,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:15.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よりによって　こんなとこで\Nいきなり会うなんてなぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,but to think I'd end up running into you here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も　お前も　うかつだな。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We've both been pretty careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:21.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで気付かなかったんだか。\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How could we not have noticed it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:25.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「ハムレット」じゃ\N妹の死後　その兄と　その恋人は→
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,715,640,688,800,1200)}In {\i1}Hamlet{\i0}, after the younger sister dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,墓地で　ばったり\N再会するじゃねぇか。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,her brother and her boyfriend reunite in a graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束だ。\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.60,0:11:37.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花の彼氏のこと聞かせろよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about Aika's boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:41.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついでに　お前の彼女のことも。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.03,0:11:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and, while we're at it, about your girlfriend too,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:46.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,話す手間は変わらないだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,since that shouldn't require any extra effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:50.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな。　まったく変わらない。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is disgusting. It's all cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:56.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずいな。\Nすっかり冷めてるじゃねぇか。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっち食べるか？\Nどっちにしても冷めてるだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Want this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:11:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All{\i0} of them are cold anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.55,0:12:01.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,というわけで→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.30,0:12:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.39,0:12:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aika's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕が愛花ちゃんの彼氏なんだよ。\Nんぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.57,0:12:07.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いきなり\N「というわけで」で済ますなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it so bluntly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.44,0:12:09.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初から　きっちり説明しろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.48,0:12:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.81,0:12:12.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,説明していいのか？\Nあっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.51,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:15.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕と愛花ちゃんが\Nいつから　つきあって→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Explaining how Aika and I began dating,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.14,0:12:17.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこに　デートに行って→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,where we went on dates,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,when we started holding hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.18,0:12:20.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どこから手をつなぐようになって\Nそして→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and even when we first kissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:22.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつごろ\Nキスをするようになったか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You kissed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.95,0:12:26.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,キスしたのか!?\Nあ…　愛花とキスしやがったのか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.76,0:12:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You k-kissed Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you do to my Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:32.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の愛花に何してやがんだ！\Nお前のじゃないって。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't belong to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.48,0:12:35.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のでもないだろ！\Nいや→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't yours either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In this case, I'd say she actually {\i1}was{\i0} mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:39.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この場合\N「僕の」という方が正しくないか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:41.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だって僕は　正真正銘→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.15,0:12:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, after all, I was her one and only boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花ちゃんの彼氏なんだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:49.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺に隠れて\Nこそこそ　つきあってたくせに→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one seeing her behind my back,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.71,0:12:53.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここへきて開き直りやがって…。\Nまあ→
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet, you have the nerve to talk to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.67,0:12:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:56.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,半殺しにされる覚悟で\N来たわけだから。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I did come here expecting you to beat me to a pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:04.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとに\Nお前が愛花の彼氏なんだよな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.73,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you really are Aika's boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.21,0:13:06.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼氏なんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.36,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:10.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それで　僕を殴らないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, you aren't going to hit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:13.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殴られるようなことしたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a reason I should?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.47,0:13:16.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほら　兄であるお前に隠れて→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I was seeing Aika behind your back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.57,0:13:18.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花ちゃんと\Nつきあってたわけだし。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,別に　兄だからって\N報告の義務はねぇよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't required to tell me just because I'm her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:26.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　愛花ちゃんだぞ？\Nじゃあ　愛花の弱み握って→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.30,0:13:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, did you do something like uncover \Nher weakness to force her to go out with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:30.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無理やりつきあってたとかなのか？\Nいや→
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:34.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に\N弱み握られてた気分だったけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.02,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, she knew {\i1}my{\i0} weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.31,0:13:37.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なら\N俺が　お前を殴る理由はねぇよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, there's no reason I should hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:41.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ん？\Nそれは　理屈に合わねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.76,0:13:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It would make no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:45.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　愛花にとって\N何者でもなかったんだからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't really anyone to Aika anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:49.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は\N愛花と友達だったわけでもねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't friends with her
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いい兄だったこともねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or a good brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:55.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兄であることすら\Nまともに認めたこともねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never even admitted to being her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:59.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ましてや　恋人でもなければ\N好きだと言ったこともねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.62,0:13:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We weren't lovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.91,0:13:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and I never told her I liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}I didn't tell Aika anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.07,0:14:04.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　何も　愛花に伝えてないんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,好きかどうかってのも→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.16,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Until recently, I hadn't even realized that I liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:09.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つい最近まで\N自覚すらしてなかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.88,0:14:12.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな自覚すらなかったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't even figure {\i1}that{\i0} out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So what gives me the right to hit the one Aika liked and was dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.68,0:14:18.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その俺が　愛花が好きで\Nつきあってたヤツを→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.07,0:14:20.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんで殴る資格がある？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.48,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.54,0:14:25.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,理屈に合わねぇ。　全然合わねぇよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,None at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ…　不合理すぎる。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.56,0:14:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's absurd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:32.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの愛花にも好きな男がいて→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If Aika actually liked someone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.25,0:14:34.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつと\N楽しく過ごせていたなら→
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.28,0:14:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and she was happy being with him,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:36.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,喜んでやるのが筋だろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.62,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I should be happy for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,especially since it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.84,0:14:39.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それが　お前なら　なおさらだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:47.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪真広は　強いな≫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.16,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You're strong, Mahiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:50.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花は　いい子だったろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aika was a good person, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, her personality was pretty horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:54.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,性格は悪かったけどね。\Nいい子だったろ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.26,0:14:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a good person, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,She had a pretty small rack though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:57.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,胸は小さかったけどね。\Nちっ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Being her boyfriend doesn't mean you get to say whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.69,0:15:01.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼氏だからって\N何を言ってもいいわけじゃねぇぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.35,0:15:09.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういや\Nお前が　富士で異常なくらい→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.51,0:15:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, when you went all out for Hakaze at Mt. Fuji,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.27,0:15:13.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,葉風に肩入れしたの\N愛花が理由か？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,was it because of Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あそこで何もしなかったら→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.36,0:15:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that if I did nothing,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.44,0:15:19.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花ちゃんの死が\N悲劇のためのものになると思った。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Aika's death would have been used only for tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.61,0:15:22.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから　それを止めようと思った。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I tried to stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.45,0:15:25.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今も\Nそのために動いてるつもりだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now, I believe that I am acting for that reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.04,0:15:31.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が　愛花ちゃんの復讐のために\N何をしようとかまわない。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.20,0:15:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what you do to get revenge for Aika's death,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:35.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　僕は　せめて\N愛花ちゃんの死によって→
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.75,0:15:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but at the very least, I want to help save the world with her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界が救われたと思える\N最後にしてみせる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:42.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,「テンペスト」…　か。\N知っているのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Tempest{\i0}, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You know it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:45.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何しろ　俺は　愛花の兄だからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.93,0:15:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I {\i1}am{\i0} Aika's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:50.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は\N愛花を殺したヤツを許す気はねぇ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of forgiving Aika's killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:53.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たとえ\Nそれで　悲劇で終わるとしてもだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,not even if it ends in tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:56.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ…　場合によっては\N僕らは敵同士か？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So depending on how things pan out, we may become enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.66,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I have an obligation to get along with her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.67,0:15:59.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花の彼氏と\N仲よくする義務もねぇだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　吉野→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But Yoshino,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:07.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前　よく愛花とつきあってたのを\N隠してられたな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you were able to hide dating Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:10.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花ちゃんが\Nしっかりしてたからね。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Aika was on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean after she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:15.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,違うだろ。　愛花が死んでからだ。\Nああ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I managed somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:18.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　なんとかね。\Nふん。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.97,0:16:21.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪無駄に強ぇヤツだよ≫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.98,Defalics,,0,0,0,,You're needlessly strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.87,0:16:25.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広こそ　よく僕を信用できるな。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.00,0:16:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you can still trust me, Mahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:28.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何がだ？\N愛花ちゃんが死んだあとも→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I continued to lead a normal life even after her death,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:31.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変わらず\N平然と暮らしてきた僕を→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気で愛花ちゃんと\Nつきあっていたかって→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I could understand if you doubted that I was dating her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:36.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,疑いそうなものだけど。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が泣くも悲しむも→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that you aren't the type
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:41.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の前ではしねぇヤツってのは\N知ってる。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,who'd cry or be sad in front of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:47.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺も　お前の前では\N泣きも　わめきも　してないだろ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,just like I wouldn't be that way in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you cried in front of someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僕の前以外じゃ\N泣いたりしたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:16:57.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（愛花）\N((こういう私を認められたら→
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.58,0:16:56.64,Defalics,,0,0,0,,When you can accept me the way I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:58.90,Defalics,,0,0,0,,you'll be a real adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:17:00.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,真広も一人前ですよ))\N((あっ…))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.29,0:17:02.86,Defalics,,0,0,0,,This, coming from a kid in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.55,0:17:03.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((中学生が生意気なこと言うな))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((その調子じゃ　お前→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:05.46,Defalics,,0,0,0,,At this rate,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:08.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,当分　彼氏はできそうにねぇな))
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:08.50,Defalics,,0,0,0,,I doubt you'll find yourself a boyfriend any time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:13.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まったく…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.50,0:17:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:17.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は　本当に　本当に→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I must really,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,愛花のことが好きなんだな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.61,0:17:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,really love Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:26.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり　１発くらい\N僕のこと殴っとくか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.63,0:17:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want to hit me, at least once?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were going to hit you, it wouldn't be just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殴るとしたら　１発で済まねぇよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.10,0:17:35.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[TEL]\N（左門）私だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It is I.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.75,0:17:38.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[TEL]（夏村）\N申し訳ありません　夏村です。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.82,0:17:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Pardon me, sir. It's Natsumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:40.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）\Nどうした。　問題が起こったか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.47,0:17:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not quite...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:43.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[TEL]（夏村）問題といいますか…。\N（左門）なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.11,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuwa Mahiro has returned to the apartment with Takigawa Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.17,0:17:46.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[TEL]（夏村）\N今　不破真広と滝川吉野が→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:49.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一緒に\Nマンションに戻ってきました。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:51.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）何ぃ!?\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.08,0:17:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A reconciliation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:54.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（左門）わ…　和解!?\N[TEL]（夏村）はい　妹の件についても→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.39,0:17:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They appear to have settled their dispute over Fuwa Mahiro's sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.58,0:17:58.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,和解が成立したようで。\N（左門）姫様は　そこにいるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the princess there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:00.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,[TEL]（夏村）あっ　いえ\N先ほど　お知らせしたところ→
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.36,0:17:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,She is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.03,0:18:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,When I informed her of the matter earlier, she seemed rather panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.92,0:18:04.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひどく慌てていらして…。\N（左門）分かった。→
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. I shall return tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:07.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私も　明日　戻る。\N何かあったら連絡をくれ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Should anything happen, inform me immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.12,0:18:14.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪本来なら　二人の和解は\N喜ぶべきことなのだが…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:14.31,Defalics,,0,0,0,,Under normal circumstances, their reconciliation would be a cause for joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪一体　どうなっている？≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:16.51,Defalics,,0,0,0,,But what in the world is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.34,0:18:20.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪私は　いつまで\Nこんなことに悩まされるのだ…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:19.47,Defalics,,0,0,0,,How much longer must I deal with such things?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:22.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）真広！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.48,0:18:25.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私の吉野に\N何もしなかったろうな!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.52,0:18:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't dare do anything to my Yoshino, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.15,0:18:29.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,してねぇよ。　あと　いつから\N吉野は　お前のものになったんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.63,0:18:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And since when is Yoshino yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:34.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）言葉のあやだ。\Nそれ　間違った使い方してねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a play on words!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.70,0:18:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think you're using the right expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:36.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）\Nなんだ？　部屋の模様替えか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.64,0:18:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're redecorating?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:39.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,２人　余計に増えたからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we need room for two more people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this becoming a girls-only bedroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この部屋は　女子専用の寝室に？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.70,0:18:45.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんなら\N私と吉野専用の寝室でもいいぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If anything, it could be {\i1}our{\i0} bedroom, Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:49.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだ？　まさか\N愛花に義理立てしてるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.13,0:18:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Are you trying to be faithful to Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.13,0:18:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If I weren't, you'd be pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.34,0:18:51.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しなかったら　お前　怒るだろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:55.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ　それで　お前を殴っても\N理屈には合うだろうな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}would{\i0} give me a reason to hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to get hit anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:19:00.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殴られるくらいで済むなら\N私に手を出せ　吉野。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you should totally play with me, Yoshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.18,0:19:04.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,存外　不破愛花より\N柔らかくてたまらんかもしれんぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll even surprise you by being more cuddly and irresistible than Fuwa Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:07.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,確かに　愛花ちゃんは\N骨っぽくて固かったですけどね。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.62,0:19:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Aika {\i1}was{\i0} kind of scrawny and hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:10.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,くっ…。\N腕も　ゴボウみたいに細くて…。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and her arms were as stringy as carrots.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい　吉野！\N（羽村）ただいま。　あっ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.11,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're home—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't compare my sister to a vegetable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人の妹を　根菜で例えるな！\Nいや　悪気はなかったんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How else could I have put it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't interfere, Mahiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.02,0:19:18.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）真広　邪魔をするな！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.11,0:19:28.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これでよかったのか？\Nさあな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right with how things ended up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.13,0:19:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:31.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前こそ　これでいいのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.55,0:19:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you? Are you okay with everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:34.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野は\Nたぶん　愛花しか見てねぇぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.62,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoshino probably has feelings only for Aika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.57,0:19:40.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）この世には\Nかなわぬ恋の方が多いものだ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,In this world, unrequited love is far too common.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:42.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,高望みはせんよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't get my hopes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに\N私は　自身の生まれと行いの→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.34,0:19:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I must take responsibility for who I am and for my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.73,0:19:47.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,責任を取らねばならん。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:51.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういや　お前\N愛花を殺した犯人を→
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you thought of a way to find Aika's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.73,0:19:54.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,見つける手を\N考えついたらしいじゃねぇか。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:20:00.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うまくいけば\N真実を目にすることができよう。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:20:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If all goes well, we should finally find out the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:05.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし　それが　どんなものであれ\N悲劇は止めねばならん。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.92,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But no matter the outcome, we must put an end to the tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,For Yoshino's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.28,0:20:09.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,吉野のためにか？\Nほかに何がある？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you don't mean it, you should say, "For the world's sake."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.20,0:20:12.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこは　うそでも\N世界のためと言っとけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:15.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,左門が泣くぞ。\N貴様が言うな。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd make Samon cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.48,0:20:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:19.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,世界のためなどより→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.15,0:20:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When you do something for the man you love instead of for the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.25,0:20:23.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほれた男のための方が\N迷わず　事を選べる。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,it's easier to decide what must be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:26.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,究極のところ　何かのためより→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ultimately, it's better to do things for someone, rather than for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰かのための方が強くあれるのだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）真広　頼むぞ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.38,0:20:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you as well, Mahiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:41.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様も誰のための戦いか\N見誤るなよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget who this battle is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:43.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.54,0:20:48.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のためにしか動かねぇよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.69,0:20:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I only act for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:53.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫（山本）最強の魔法使い様が→
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The invincible mage seems to be wearing a rather helpless expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:56.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんとも\N頼りない顔してるじゃないの。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:21:00.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,みんな　信念に従って\N行動してるのは分かります。
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:21:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that everyone's acting on their feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:05.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも　何が正しいのか\N分からなくなっちゃって。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can't tell right from wrong anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:11.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）そうね。\N真広君　吉野君　葉風さん→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.60,0:21:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.29,0:21:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mahiro, Yoshino, Miss Hakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:13.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの三人は強いけれど→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.32,0:21:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of them are strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.60,0:21:15.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,彼らが未来に願うのは→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but what they want from the future
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:18.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,所詮　かなわない夢なのよ。→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is something that cannot come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:20.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失ったものに未練ばかり残し→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They remain attached to what was lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.97,0:21:24.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き止まりに向かって走るだけ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and keep running into dead ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:27.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,死人に足をつかまれた子たちに\N従うのが→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.14,0:21:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it's the right thing to listen to those haunted by the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:32.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,果たして正しいかしらね？\Nじゃあ　左門さんと早河さんは？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.28,0:21:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, what about Mr. Samon and Mr. Hayakawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.32,0:21:35.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの二人は　なるべく\N多くの人間が生き残る選択を→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doing their best to ensure the highest possible number of survivors,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しようとはしているけど→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but they also don't care how many lives must be sacrificed in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.67,0:21:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのためには　どんな犠牲が出ても\Nかまわないとも思ってる。→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.51,0:21:44.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな連中が正しいなんて→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether that's the right thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:48.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は　とても言えないわ～。\N笑い事じゃないですって。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.25,0:21:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say for sure either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't something to laugh about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.45,0:21:51.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（山本）そうね。\Nでも　それぞれの正義なんて→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,True, but if you change perspectives, you can make a joke of anyone's sense of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:55.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,立場が変われば\Nただの悪い冗談よ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.27,0:21:58.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,要は　君自身は\Nなんのために戦うか。→
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.57,0:21:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What matters is what {\i1}you{\i0} want to fight for.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それだけ決めときなさい。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to decide on that for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.22,0:22:07.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）最後の果実を飛ばす前に\N確かめねばならんことがある。→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Before we get the last fruit to fly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.48,0:22:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,there is something I need to confirm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.69,0:22:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it that killed Fuwa Aika?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:10.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一体\N誰が不破愛花を殺したのか。→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.84,0:22:13.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あるいは\Nそこに　今の混乱した状況と→
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,At the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.88,0:22:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we'll discover the truth behind the two Trees, \Nand what caused the current confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.88,0:22:16.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,二つの大樹の\N真実があるとも思える。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.06,0:22:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I'm planning to return to the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:22.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（葉風）そこで\N私は再び　過去に戻ろうと思う。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:26.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,不破愛花の殺される前の時間にな。
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to a time before Fuwa Aika was killed!
